**ULIP (Unit Linked Insurance Plan)** combines life insurance with market-linked investments. However, multiple layers of charges — mortality charges, premium allocation charges (5–8%), fund management charges (1.35% cap), policy admin charges — significantly reduce effective returns compared to a pure term insurance + mutual fund combination. This calculator shows your actual post-charge return.
